Chroma-Grit Sketch.png.title: Chroma-Grit Sketch
Chroma-Grit Sketch.png.description: 颗粒质感与速写线条，即兴氛围强，适合草图与概念探索的自由视觉。
Chroma-Grit Sketch.png.keywords: 颗粒速写,即兴,手绘,质感噪点
Chroma-Grit Sketch.png.prompt: A gritty neon sketchbook spread filled with fast scribbled strokes, chalk dust, and rough marker trails glowing against a dark background.

Lo-fi Chibi.png.title: Lo-fi Chibi
Lo-fi Chibi.png.description: 低保真颗粒感与柔和色调，Chill 气质的 Q 版角色搭配复古滤镜。
Lo-fi Chibi.png.keywords: 低保真,颗粒感,治愈,Chill,柔和色调
Lo-fi Chibi.png.prompt: A small chibi character listening to music on a rainy night with VHS grain and soft lo-fi colors.

Luminous Bloom.png.title: Luminous Bloom
Luminous Bloom.png.description: 柔光与高光溢出营造梦幻纯净的 Bloom 特效，强调圣洁氛围。
Luminous Bloom.png.keywords: 柔光,高光溢出,梦幻,纯净,Bloom特效
Luminous Bloom.png.prompt: An ethereal angel portrait with extreme soft focus and strong lens bloom glow, luminous bloom style.

Visual Novel .png.title: Visual Novel
Visual Novel .png.description: 高分辨率赛璐珞上色、角色细腻，背景强调氛围光效与饱和色彩，常配合对话框布局。
Visual Novel .png.keywords: 赛璐珞,氛围光,静态特写,高分辨率,日系CG
Visual Novel .png.prompt: A female character with detailed anime eyes and hair, standing in a dimly lit classroom, high-resolution cel shading, visual novel game CG.

Rotoscoped Animation.png.title: Rotoscoped Animation
Rotoscoped Animation.png.description: 根据真人拍摄路径逐帧描摹，线条清晰且动作真实流畅，保留独特运动轨迹。
Rotoscoped Animation.png.keywords: 真实动作,流畅线条,描绘轮廓,运动写实,黑边描绘
Rotoscoped Animation.png.prompt: A figure dancing dynamically in a spotlight, traced and animated from real footage, fluid motion, strong black outlines, rotoscoping style.

Cutout Animation.png.title: Cutout Animation
Cutout Animation.png.description: 剪纸/卡纸材质与平面拼贴质感，粗糙边缘与块状元素，二维层次运动。
Cutout Animation.png.keywords: 剪纸,卡纸,平面拼贴,二维运动,粗糙边缘
Cutout Animation.png.prompt: A large monster made of multicolored cardboard chasing a smaller character, visible paper edges, cutout animation style.

Sand Animation.png.title: Sand Animation
Sand Animation.png.description: 背光板上的沙子颗粒与即兴流动，画面持续变形，呈现流沙墨迹效果。
Sand Animation.png.keywords: 沙子颗粒,流动,即兴,背光,艺术表演
Sand Animation.png.prompt: The silhouette of a ship morphing into a bird on a light table with fine sand, granular texture, sand animation art.

Expressionist Sketch.png.title: Expressionist Sketch
Expressionist Sketch.png.description: 夸张形体与粗犷笔触，扭曲透视及非自然色彩，强调强烈情绪。
Expressionist Sketch.png.keywords: 夸张形体,粗犷笔触,非自然色彩,强烈情感,速写
Expressionist Sketch.png.prompt: A figure screaming with violently distorted perspective, thick aggressive lines, unsettling color palette, expressionist sketch style.

Surreal Cartoon.png.title: Surreal Cartoon
Surreal Cartoon.png.description: 梦境般的逻辑颠倒与达利式变形，幽默抽象的卡通组合带来强烈冲击。
Surreal Cartoon.png.keywords: 逻辑颠倒,梦境,奇特组合,抽象,达利式变形
Surreal Cartoon.png.prompt: A melting clock draped over a floating geometric building under a bizarre dreamy sky, humorous distortion, surreal cartoon style.

Art Nouveau Line.png.title: Art Nouveau Line
Art Nouveau Line.png.description: 新艺术运动的装饰性线条与优雅曲线，平面化柔和色彩搭配藤蔓图案。
Art Nouveau Line.png.keywords: 装饰性线条,曲线优雅,平面化,复古优雅
Art Nouveau Line.png.prompt: A woman with flowing hair framed by intricate decorative plant motifs and stylized curves, elegant Art Nouveau illustration style.

Constructivism Poster.png.title: Constructivism Poster
Constructivism Poster.png.description: 几何结构与强烈斜线构图，红黑白工业美学营造宣传海报力量感。
Constructivism Poster.png.keywords: 几何图形,强斜线,红黑白,工业美学,结构力量
Constructivism Poster.png.prompt: An industrial worker formed by hard geometric shapes and sharp diagonal lines in red, black and white, constructivist poster design.

Cel Shading.png.title: Cel Shading
Cel Shading.png.description: 3D 模型使用平坦硬朗阴影分层，线条清晰，让画面像 2D 赛璐珞动画。
Cel Shading.png.keywords: 3D卡通,硬阴影,赛璐珞光影,清晰线条
Cel Shading.png.prompt: A detailed 3D robot warrior rendered with hard flat blocks of shadow and sharp outlines, cel shading render.

Isometric Pixel Art.png.title: Isometric Pixel Art
Isometric Pixel Art.png.description: 等距 45° 像素视角呈现立体空间，适合城市/建筑全景展示。
Isometric Pixel Art.png.keywords: 等距视角,像素化,45度角,立体空间
Isometric Pixel Art.png.prompt: A cozy cafe scene in perfect 45-degree isometric pixel art showing the full interior layout.

Cyberpunk Anime.png.title: Cyberpunk Anime
Cyberpunk Anime.png.description: 霓虹蓝紫红配色、湿润街道与强阴影，构成高科技低生活的夜景氛围。
Cyberpunk Anime.png.keywords: 霓虹,高对比,湿润街道,强阴影,未来
Cyberpunk Anime.png.prompt: A lone figure on a neon-drenched futuristic street, high contrast blues and magentas with rain reflections, cyberpunk anime.

Americana Vintage.png.title: Americana Vintage
Americana Vintage.png.description: 30 年代橡胶软管风格，低饱和或黑白画面配夸张喜剧动作与胶片颗粒。
Americana Vintage.png.keywords: 橡胶软管,黑白,30s动画,夸张动作,复古美式
Americana Vintage.png.prompt: A cartoon with rubber hose limbs and pie-cut eyes in a grainy black-and-white scene, 1930s Americana cartoon style.
